// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0879 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 45f89b49-c5b1-5d78-8da2-bea7aebfa964

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
